Titolo: Astroneer

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Astroneer is a sandbox adventure game developed by System Era Softworks. The game was released through early access in December 2016 before a full release in 2019. The player is tasked with colonizing planets, creating structures, and collecting resources. Astroneer has no set goal or storyline, though each planet holds challenges for players to complete.

Genere: Sandbox 

Valutazione: 73
